scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Two metal keys [unlabeled]; wooden plaque with Altrusa symbol and names of Lexington club member; glass ashtray celebrating Golden Anniversary (1917-1967); Piece of ash wood, labeled "'Ash' from Ashland," presented by Dean F. P. Anderson; Ila Earle Fowler award medallion, 1951.
